Aknowlegement

Lunch time

The Charity trustees would like to express their gratitude to Teklehaimanot Derso in Addis Ababa who developed the website for EOS-UK Charity Fund gratis.

They would also like to thank Tesfai Hailu, Programme Manager at Elshadai Wukro Children's Village (EWCV), for checking the information compiled for building the web pages.
